  "lyric": "早晨的阳光照在窗台<br>\n这歌谣  像无人看管的小孩儿<br>\n如果我的心被分成两半<br>\n一半去流浪 一半去陪你<br>\n<br>\n昨夜你突然起来叫我<br>\n递给我一个苹果 带我看你的房间<br>\n你懂得明白我的感受是多么容易<br>\n因为你只是想让我说一句：我漂亮吗？<br>\n吻我，就深深地吻我吧<br>\n为了你的白天和黑夜我会在这儿<br>\n我知道你不相信天使的存在<br>\n那么请你把我搂在你的怀中<br>\n<br>\n当我低头微笑时你仿佛说：亲亲<br>\n“要喝点儿什么嘛，威士忌？”<br>\n“哦，那真是太好了，我正愁得睡不着呢”<br>\n“干了这杯酒，我下药的酒你能不醉？”<br>\n吻我，就深深地吻我吧<br>\n为了你的白天和黑夜我会在这儿<br>\n我知道你不相信天使的存在<br>\n你不是一个容易隐藏情绪的主儿<br>\n吻我，就深深地吻我吧<br>\n为了你的白天和黑夜我会在这儿<br>\n我知道你不相信天使的存在<br>\n那么请你把我搂在能的怀中<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nThe Morning Sunlight <br>\nComposer/Lyrics: Zuoxiao Zuzhou<br>\n<br>\nThe morning light shines upon the balcony,<br>\nThis ballad, is like a small child that has never been watched over.<br>\nIf my heart breaks into two,<br>\nOne half would stray, one half would accompany you.<br>\n<br>\nLast night you suddenly got up and called for me,<br>\nHanded me an apple, brought me to see your room.<br>\nDo you understand how my emotions are so easy,<br>\nBecause you kept wanting me to say one sentence: am I beautiful?<br>\nKiss me, just kiss me deeply,<br>\nFor your day and night, I will be here.<br>\nI know you don’t believe in the existence of angels,<br>\nThen please take me into your bosom and hug me.<br>\n<br>\nWhen I was looking down and smiling, you seem to say: dearie, <br>\n“Want to drink something, whiskey?”<br>\n“Oh, that would be great, I was just worrying that I wouldn’t be able to sleep”<br>\n“Finish this cup of alcohol, this alcohol that I has drugged, it’s a wonder if you’re not drunk?”<br>\nKiss me, just kiss me deeply,<br>\nFor your day and night, I will be here.<br>\nI know you don’t believe in the existence of angels,<br>\nYou are not a master that can easily conceal feelings.<br>\nKiss me, just kiss me deeply,<br>\nFor your day and night, I will be here.<br>\nI know you don’t believe in the existence of angels,<br>\nThen please take me into your bosom and hug me.",
